items.name: ASSORTED SIX
items.description: Mix & Match Box of 6 (Random Flavours Given)

items.name: Chunky Chocolate Chip
items.description: Indulge in the ultimate chocolate chip cookie experience with our mouthwatering chunky chocolate chip cookies. Made with the finest belgian chocolate, these cookies boast rich, velvety chocolate chunks that melt in your mouth with every bite.

items.name: Dark Chocolate Overloaded
items.description: Brace yourself for a cocoa-infused journey like no other. This cookie is a chocolate lover's dream with the rich intensity of dark chocolate. Every bite is a harmonious blend of decadent flavors and textures that will send your taste buds into pure bliss.

items.name: Chunky Chip Walnut
items.description: Twist on the classic chocolate chip cookie. Indulge in the nostalgic flavors of the good ole' chocolate chip cookie, enhanced with the rich and nutty goodness of walnuts.

items.name: Matcha Lava
items.description: Enchant your taste buds with the allure of our Matcha Lava Stuffed Matcha Cookie.This mouthwatering delight is sure to captivate your senses and leave you craving more. With its soft and decadent matcha core and crisp cookie exterior, be enchanted from the first bite.

items.name: Hojicha Lava
items.description:
Hojicha Lava Stuffed Hojicha Cookie
Soft baked Hojicha cookie with oozing hojicha lava

items.name: Dark Cocoa Speculoos Cookie
items.description: Immerse yourself in the decadent allure of rich dark cocoa dough embracing a melty and gooey caramelized cookie speculoos filling. With every bite, you'll discover the perfect balance of intense dark cocoa flavor and the indulgent sweetness of the speculoos filling.

items.name: Oatmeal Raisin
items.description: Made from wholesome oats & plump, juicy raisins & a tinge of cinnamon, these cookies are a delightful blend of chewy & crispy textures.Our homemade Oatmeal Raisin Cookies offer a nostalgic taste of tradition, baked to perfection for a delicious treat any time of day.

items.name: Crème Brûlée Cookie
items.description: Crème Brûlée Cookie, where our classic cookie dough envelops a luscious Crème Brûlée pudding speckled with Madagascar Bourbon vanilla beans. With each bite, you'll experience the perfect fusion of flavors and textures.

items.name: Chocolate Smores
items.description: These mouthwatering cookies are crafted with love, a delectable combination of rich chocolate, crunchy graham cracker crumbs, and a gooey marshmallow center that will transport you straight to your favorite fireside memories.

items.name: Salted Dark Chocolate Brownie
items.description: Indulge in the ultimate chocolatey delight that will leave you craving for more. Made with premium Belgian dark chocolate, this brownie is a decadent masterpiece that showcases the richness and depth of flavor that only high-quality belgian chocolate can deliver.

items.name: Speculoos Delight Brownie
items.description: Our favourite cookie butter stuffed into a brownie. Delightful!

items.name: Matcha Cocoa Brownie
items.description: Umami matcha fillin' hidden in it's belly

items.name: Raspberry Dark Chocolate Brownie
items.description: Filled with dark chocolate raspberry ganache, topped with Valrhona dark raspberry chocolate.

items.name: Gimmie Smore Brownie
items.description: The perfect blend of marshmallows and biscuit crumbs will take your taste buds on a delicious adventure. This delectable treat starts with a rich and fudgy chocolate brownie base, topped with a layer of gooey marshmallows that add a touch of creamy sweetness.

items.name: Oreo Peanut Butter Brownie
items.description: Swirled with creamy peanut butter and loaded with Oreo cookies!
